# Copy standards

- Use typographic apostrophe `’` in user-facing text. Do not use escaped apostrophes like `\'`.
- For any new user-facing string, add string in:
  - `values/strings.xml`
- Keep existing behavior tests meaningful: avoid duplicate assertions that check the same text for different test methods.
